data.description: Stunning Two Story Home, 3500 square ft, 5 bedroom, 4 baths, 3 car garage and RV parking, beautifully updated, sits on .48-acre lot, situated in Paint Brush Hills Subdivision. Covered Entry welcomes with new Luxury Vinyl on main level and an abundance of natural lighting throughout the home. Great room with vaulted ceiling and built-ins leading to the formal dining room with bay window which flows seamlessly into the remodeled kitchen with granite counters, all new cabinets w/soft close feature and pull-out drawers, breakfast & coffee bar, farm sink, and stainless-steel appliances. From the kitchen ease into the large family room with gas burning fireplace, built-ins and walk-out to an enormous backyard. Oversized laundry room with cabinets/shelving and ½ bath completes the main. The upper level with new carpeting does not disappoint with huge Primary Suite w/vaulted ceiling, large walk-in closet and 5-piece bath with jetted tub. In addition to the Primary Suite, the upper level contains two generously sized bedrooms and a full bath. 1262 Square Ft. basement offers a Huge 16X32 family room, two sizable bedrooms and updated ¾ bath. Upgrades include: new Luxury Vinyl flooring, carpet, paint, appliances, granite in kitchen and baths, light fixtures, and recessed lighting. Some features include: Dual zoned heating and air, smart lights and thermostat, Vaulted ceilings, and farm sink. Class 4 shingled room replaced in 2022. The last Radon report 5/8/2022 is available upon request.
